            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Wash your<strong> pak choi</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper, then rip the <strong>green leaves</strong> from your <strong>pak choi </strong>and set them aside</p><p>Chop the <strong>white base</strong> into rough, large pieces</p><p>Slice your<strong> red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
