      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef mince has browned slightly, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> chopped pak choi white base </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
