    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>red chilli relish </strong>and <strong>cornflour</strong> in a small bowl with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
