      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>stir-fry sauce</strong>,<strong> pak choi leaves</strong> and <strong>drained noodles </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1 min until the sauce has started to coat the noodles and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>Asian-style beef & pak choi noodles</strong></p>",
