    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Asian-style beef & pak choi noodles</strong></p><p>Tear over your <strong>coriander</strong> and garnish with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
